| Hero title (marketing only) | `font-heading font-bold`, `clamp(2.25rem, 2.6vw + 1rem, 3.6rem)` | Montserrat |
| Page H1 (product pages) | `text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold` | Montserrat |
