## 5. Spacing System (8px grid)

All spacing maps to the Tailwind scale. Never use arbitrary pixel values that don't align.

```
4px  = 1    (gap-1, p-1)
8px  = 2    (gap-2, p-2)
12px = 3    (gap-3, p-3)
16px = 4    (gap-4, p-4)
20px = 5    (gap-5, p-5)
24px = 6    (gap-6, p-6)
32px = 8    (gap-8, p-8)
48px = 12   (gap-12, py-12)
64px = 16   (py-16)
```

