## 8. CTA Hierarchy

Each section gets at most 1 primary CTA visible at a time.

| Level | Style |
|---|---|
| Primary (solid) | `bg-[var(--ff-color-primary-700)] text-white rounded-xl hover:bg-[var(--ff-color-primary-600)]` |
| Secondary (outline) | `bg-transparent border border-[var(--color-border)] text-[var(--color-text)] rounded-xl` |
| Tertiary | Icon-only (`IconButton`), text link, or ghost button |

**Focus ring** (all interactive): `focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-[var(--ff-color-primary-600)] focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-none`

**Touch target**: minimum `w-11 h-11` (44x44px) for every button, link, and interactive element.

Never stack two primary CTAs side by side. Never put a primary CTA on a badge/pill.

