## 10. Badge / Pill Rules

Badges are supporting elements. They must never compete with titles or CTAs.

- Size: always `text-xs`
- Shape: always `rounded-full`
- Max 2 per metadata row
- Background: soft tints only (via `color-mix()\` or token)
- Text: `var(--color-text)\` or `var(--color-muted)`
- Never: bold text, large size, high-contrast fill, primary-700 background

