## 13. Responsive Breakpoints

Mobile-first. Always. Desktop classes extend mobile.

| Breakpoint | Tailwind | Use |
|---|---|---|
| Default | (none) | Mobile layout, single column |
| `sm:` | 640px | Two-column grids, expanded padding |
| `md:` | 768px | Three-column grids, tablet adjustments |
| `lg:` | 1024px | Desktop layout, max-width activation |
| `xl:` | 1280px | Rarely ŌĆö only for very wide marketing sections |

