## 14. Accessibility (WCAG AA)

Non-negotiable on every page:

- Skip link: `<a href="#main-content">\` on every page
- Semantic HTML: `<main>`, `<section aria-labelledby>`, `<nav aria-label>`, `<h1>`-`<h6>` in order
- Keyboard navigation: all interactive elements focusable and operable
- Focus ring: `focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-[var(--ff-color-primary-600)] focus-visible:ring-offset-2`
- Color contrast: 4.5:1 minimum for body text, 3:1 for large text
- Touch targets: 44x44px minimum (`w-11 h-11`)
- Alt text: descriptive for content images, `aria-hidden="true"\` for decorative
- Aria labels: on all icon-only buttons, on all interactive elements without visible text

