## 18. Stop Conditions

STOP all changes immediately and report a recovery plan if you detect:
- 2 headers/navbars in the DOM
- Zero styling on a component (unstyled render)
- Legacy amber/stone Tailwind color classes outside tokens
- Import or glob errors
- Unknown or broken routes
- Node-only imports in client code
- Token violations: hex/rgb/hsl values in `src/**`
- Business logic changes when only UI was requested

