## 19. Output Standard

After every task, respond with:

**SHIP**: What was changed (file paths + concise bullets).
**WHY**: Why this was the right approach.
**SUGGEST_NEXT**:
  - **Improve**: concrete improvements on what was just delivered (UX/a11y/perf/SEO/refactor).
  - **Feature**: if nothing to improve, propose new functionality that elevates FitFi.
**GUARDRAILS**: Confirm tokens-compliance, 1 Navbar, no Node-only imports.

